224
00:13:32,622 --> 00:13:34,022
Si, huele bien.

225
00:13:34,123 --> 00:13:36,323
Dicen que elimina la caspa, pero...

226
00:13:36,324 --> 00:13:38,224
...no estoy segura, mira...

227
00:13:38,525 --> 00:13:39,725
